tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE keyword_rankings (
  keyword_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  keyword VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  ranking_position INT,
  search_volume INT,
  competition_level FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE seo_metrics (
    metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword_id UUID REFERENCES keyword_rankings(keyword_id),
    search_volume INT NOT NULL,
    average_cpc DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    organic_traffic INT
);

CREATE TABLE RankingsHistory (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    website_id INT,
    keyword_id INT,
    ranking_position INT,
    ranking_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_rankings (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    rank_position INT NOT NULL,
    website VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    search_engine VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_rankings (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    rank INTEGER NOT NULL,
    search_engine VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    date_updated DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE website_performance (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    website_url VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    organic_traffic INTEGER NOT NULL,
    total_visits INTEGER NOT NULL,
    bounce_rate DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    conversion_rate DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_stats (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
    average_rank INTEGER NOT NULL,
    monthly_search_volume INTEGER NOT NULL,
    competition_level VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE competitor_analysis (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    organic_traffic INTEGER NOT NULL,
    backlinks INTEGER NOT NULL,
    total_keywords_ranking INTEGER NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE seo_agency (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    agency_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    team_size INTEGER NOT NULL,
    clients_served INTEGER NOT NULL
);
